lead_paragraph: Inter Milan appointed journeyman Stefano Pioli on Tuesday as their ninth coach in the last six years, his first managerial role with one of Italy's top three clubs.

headline.print_headline: Pioli Becomes Inter Milan's Ninth Coach in Six Years
